#: ../../talk/chat.rst:3
msgid "Sending messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí a sheoladh"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:6
msgid "Using Markdown"
msgstr "Ag Úsáid Markdown"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can enhance your messages using Markdown syntax. Supported elements:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do theachtaireachtaí a fheabhsú trí chomhréir Markdown a "
"úsáid. Eilimintí tacaithe:"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:10
msgid "**Headings and dividers**"
msgstr "**Ceannteidil agus roinnteoirí**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:27
msgid "**Inline decorations**"
msgstr "**Maisiúcháin inlíne**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:40
msgid "**Lists**"
msgstr "**Liostaí**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:51
msgid "**Quotes**"
msgstr "**Sleachta**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:58
msgid "**Task lists**"
msgstr "**Liostaí tascanna**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:65
msgid "**Tables**"
msgstr "**Táblaí**"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:74
msgid "Inserting emoji"
msgstr "Emoji á chur isteach"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:76
msgid ""
"You can add emoji using the picker on the left of the text input field."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat emoji a chur leis trí úsáid a bhaint as an roghnóir ar chlé "
"an réimse ionchuir téacs."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:82
msgid "Smart Picker"
msgstr "Roghnóir Cliste"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:84
msgid ""
"The smart picker makes it easier to insert links, files, or other content "
"into your conversations. Just choose the type of content you want to insert "
"(files, Talk conversations, Deck cards, GIFs, etc.). You can also type `/` "
"in the chat input to open the selector."
msgstr ""
"Leis an roghnóir cliste, is fusa naisc, comhaid, nó ábhar eile a chur "
"isteach i do chomhráite. Níl le déanamh ach an cineál ábhair is mian leat a "
"roghnú (comhaid, comhráite Talk, cártaí Deic, GIFanna, srl.). Is féidir leat"
" `/` a chlóscríobh san ionchur comhrá freisin chun an roghnóir a oscailt."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:94
msgid "Replying to messages and more"
msgstr "Freagairt a thabhairt ar theachtaireachtaí agus tuilleadh"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:96
msgid ""
"You can reply to a message using the arrow that appears when you hover a "
"message."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat freagra a thabhairt ar theachtaireacht trí úsáid a bhaint as "
"an tsaighead a thaispeántar nuair a luíonn tú an luch thar theachtaireacht."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:101
msgid ""
"In the ``...`` menu you can also choose to reply privately. This will open a"
" one-to-one conversation."
msgstr ""
"Sa roghchlár ``...`` is féidir leat rogha a dhéanamh freagra a thabhairt go "
"príobháideach freisin. Osclóidh sé seo comhrá duine le duine."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:106
msgid ""
"Here you can also create a direct link to the message or mark it unread so "
"you will scroll back there next time you enter the chat. When it is a file, "
"you can view the file in Files."
msgstr ""
"Anseo is féidir leat nasc díreach a chruthú chuig an teachtaireacht nó é a "
"mharcáil mar neamhléite ionas go mbeidh tú in ann scrollú ar ais ann an "
"chéad uair eile a théann tú isteach sa chomhrá. Nuair atá sé ina chomhad, is"
" féidir leat an comhad a fheiceáil i gComhaid."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:109
msgid "Silent messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí ciúine"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:111
msgid ""
"If you don't want to disturb anyone in the middle of the night, there is a "
"silent mode for chatting. While it is enabled, other participants will not "
"receive notifications from your messages."
msgstr ""
"Mura mian leat cur isteach ar aon duine i lár na hoíche, tá mód ciúin ann le"
" haghaidh comhrá. Cé go bhfuil sé cumasaithe, ní bhfaighidh rannpháirtithe "
"eile fógraí ó do theachtaireachtaí."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:118
msgid "Scheduling messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí a sceidealú"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:120
msgid ""
"If you want to send a message not right now, but at a specific time, you can"
" schedule it. Just select the desired date and time in the quick actions "
"next to the input field."
msgstr ""
"Más mian leat teachtaireacht a sheoladh ag am ar leith, ní láithreach, is "
"féidir leat í a sceidealú. Níl le déanamh ach an dáta agus an t-am atá uait "
"a roghnú sna gníomhartha tapa in aice leis an réimse ionchuir."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:125
msgid ""
"You can find all your scheduled messages by clicking on the clock icon next "
"to the input field. There you can edit, reschedule or delete currently "
"prepared messages."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do theachtaireachtaí sceidealaithe go léir a fháil trí "
"chliceáil ar dheilbhín an chloig in aice leis an réimse ionchuir. Ansin is "
"féidir leat teachtaireachtaí atá ullmhaithe faoi láthair a chur in eagar, a "
"athsceidealú nó a scriosadh."

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:131
msgid "Chat summary"
msgstr "Achoimre ar an gcomhrá"

#: ../../talk/chat.rst:133
msgid ""
"When AI assistant is enabled, a summary can be generated for a conversation "
"if there are more than 100 unread messages. You can generate it by pressing "
"the button that is visible in chat above the first unread messages."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn cúntóir AI cumasaithe, is féidir achoimre a ghiniúint do "
"chomhrá má tá níos mó ná 100 teachtaireacht neamhléite ann. Is féidir leat é"
" a ghiniúint tríd an gcnaipe atá le feiceáil sa chomhrá os cionn na chéad "
"teachtaireachtaí neamhléite a bhrú."
